'''萨莉·克里斯滕·莱德博士'''（{{lang|en|'''Dr Sally Kristen Ride'''}}，{{bd|1951年|5月26日|2012年|7月23日|catIdx=R}}）是一位美国[[物理学家|物理学家]]，曾是[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]的[[宇航员|宇航员]]，执行过[[STS-7|STS-7]]以及[[STS-41-G|STS-41-G]]任务。她在1978年加入[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]（NASA），并于1983年32岁时成为第一个进入太空的美国女性<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=http://science.ksc.nasa.gov/pao/faq/faqanswers.htm |title=Kennedy Space Center FAQ |publisher=NASA/Kennedy Space Center External Relations and Business Development Directorate |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2016-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122162626/http://science.ksc.nasa.gov/pao/faq/faqanswers.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=10 fascinating things about Astronaut Sally Ride you must know|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2015/05/10-awesome-things-about-astronaut-sally-ride-you-must-know/|accessdate=2015-05-26|publisher=news.biharprabha.com|date=2015-05-26|archive-date=2015-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526093244/http://news.biharprabha.com/2015/05/10-awesome-things-about-astronaut-sally-ride-you-must-know/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，也是人類史上第三位女性太空人。1987年，她离开了美国国家航空航天局在[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]国际安全和军备控制中心工作，后来到[[加利福尼亞大學聖地牙哥分校|加利福尼亞大學聖地牙哥分校]]担任物理学教授，主要研究[[非线性光学|非线性光学]]和[[汤姆孙散射|汤姆孙散射]]。莱德是唯一一位同时参与过[[挑战者号航天飞机|挑战者号航天飞机]]和[[哥伦比亚号航天飞机|哥伦比亚号航天飞机]]事故调查委员会的人<ref name=obit>{{cite news |last=Grady |first=Denise |title=Obituary: American Woman Who Shattered Space Ceiling|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/24/science/space/sally-ride-trailblazing-astronaut-dies-at-61.html?pagewanted=all |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2012-07-23 |access-date=2012-07-27}}</ref><ref>See [[Rogers_Commission_Report|Rogers Commission Report]] and [[Columbia_Accident_Investigation_Board|Columbia Accident Investigation Board]]</ref>。截至2015年，她依然是进入太空时最年轻的美国宇航员<ref name="#1"/>。

莱德去世后，在讣告中公开了她的同性伴侣湯·奧肖內西（Tam O'Shaughnessy）。這使莱德成为第一个公开[[出櫃|出櫃]]的同性恋宇航员<ref>White, Madeleine (July 24, 2012). [http://www.theglobeandmail.com/life/the-hot-button/remembering-sally-ride-americas-first-woman-and-lesbian-to-fly-in-space/article4437138/ "Remembering Sally Ride: America's first woman (and lesbian) to fly in space"]. ''[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]''. Retrieved July 25, 2012.</ref><ref>Seltzer, Sarah (July 24, 2012). [http://www.alternet.org/newsandviews/article/1048109/r.i.p_sally_ride,_first_woman_%28and_lesbian%29_in_space/ "R.I.P Sally Ride, First Woman (and Lesbian) In Space"]. [[AlterNet|AlterNet]]. Retrieved July 25, 2012.</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Sally Ride Was Also The First Lesbian In Space |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/sally-ride-was-also-the-first-lesbian-in-space-2012-7 |date=2012-07-24 |publisher=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]] |accessdate=2012-07-24 }}</ref>，也是第一個公開出櫃的女同性戀太空人。

== 早期生活 ==
萨莉·莱德出生于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]恩奇诺，具有[[挪威|挪威]]血统。她有一个妹妹，是[[长老教会|长老教会]]的牧师。父母都是[[长老教会|长老教会]]的长老。她的父亲一直在圣莫尼卡学院担任政治学教授<ref name=obit />。
她高中在[[洛杉矶联合学区|洛杉矶联合学区]]和[[哈佛西湖学校|西湖女子学校]]学习并获得奖学金<ref name=obit />。除了对科学感兴趣，她还曾是一位[[网球|网球]]选手，从10岁起就开始练习打网球，也想成为一名职业运动员，但最终放弃。在[[斯沃斯莫爾學院|斯沃斯莫爾學院]]学习了三个学期后，又在[[加州大学洛杉矶分校|加州大学洛杉矶分校]]学习物理课程，而后进入[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]，获得[[物理|物理]]及[[英文|英文]][[学士|学士]]學位，随后获得物理学硕士学位和博士学位，主要研究[[天体物理学|天体物理学]]和[[自由电子激光|自由电子激光]]物理学<ref name="ride1">{{cite web|url=http://www.jsc.nasa.gov/Bios/htmlbios/ride-sk.html|title=Sally K. Ride, Ph.D Biography|accessdate=2007-10-04|publisher=NASA|year=2006|author=NASA|archive-date=2007-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016072450/http://www.jsc.nasa.gov/Bios/htmlbios/ride-sk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 航天生涯 ==
[[file:Ride_on_the_Middeck_-_GPN-2000-001081.jpg|thumb]]执行[[STS-7|STS-7]]任务]]
1977年，[[美國國家航空暨太空總署|美國國家航空暨太空總署]]太空人徵選首次開放平民與女性參加，她前往應徵，獲得錄取。她是斯坦福大学申请参加[[航天机构列表|太空计划]]的8000名学生之一<ref name="starchild">{{cite web |url=http://starchild.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/StarChild/whos_who_level2/ride.html |title=Dr. Sally Ride |access-date=2015-05-11 |publisher=NASA |archive-date=2015-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150517063049/http://starchild.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/StarChild/whos_who_level2/ride.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1978年莱德正式加入[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]<ref name=autogenerated1/>。她开始为第二次和第三次航天飞机飞行（STS-2和STS-3）进行地面通信工作，并帮助开发了航天飞机的机械臂<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite web |last=Ryan |first=Michael |url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20085312,00.html |title=A Ride in Space – NASA, Sally Ride |publisher=People.com |date= |accessdate=2013-12-05 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413131850/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20085312,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1983年6月18日，她參與[[挑戰者號|挑戰者號]]任務（[[STS-7|STS-7]]），成為第一位美國女太空人。也是继苏联1963年的[[瓦莲京娜·捷列什科娃|瓦莲京娜·捷列什科娃]]和1982年的[[斯維特蘭娜·薩維茨卡婭|斯維特蘭娜·薩維茨卡婭]]之后第三位女性宇航员。STS-7任务的五人小组部署了两颗通信卫星，并进行了药品试验。莱德是第一位在太空使用机械臂和检索[[人造衛星|人造衛星]]的人<ref name="ride1"/>。

1984年她的第二次太空飞行也是挑战者号任务。她在太空的时间超过343小时。莱德在完成8个月的训练后，准备参加她的第三次飞行（STS-61-M，一个TDRS部署任务），后因挑战者号航天飞机失事而中断。随后她被任命为[[罗杰斯委员会|罗杰斯委员会]]（总统调查事故委员会）领导小组的成员<ref name="ride1"/>。调查结束之后，莱德被分配到总部设在[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]的国家航空航天局，在那里她带领美国航空航天局进行了第一个[[战略计划|战略计划]]工作，撰写了题为“美国航空航天局的领导和美国在太空的未来”的报告，并建立了美国宇航局探索办公室<ref name="ride1"/>。
{{-}}
==离开NASA以后==
1987年，莱德离开华盛顿来到斯坦福大学国际安全和军备控制中心工作。1989年，她成为加州大学聖地牙哥分校的物理学教授并指导加州太空研究所。从90年代中期直到她去世，莱德与美国航天局喷气推进实验室和加州大学聖地牙哥分校合作领导了两次NASA的公众宣传计划 -ISS EarthKAM和GRAIL MoonKAM项目。该项目允许中学生征求地球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://earthkam.ucsd.edu/about/ |title=EarthKAM (Earth Knowledge Acquired by Middle school students) |publisher=Sally Ride Science |accessdate=2012-07-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120729152535/https://earthkam.ucsd.edu/about |archivedate=2012-07-29}}</ref>和月球图像<ref>{{cite web|url=http://moonkam.ucsd.edu/about/moonkam |title=GRAIL MoonKAM (Moon Knowledge Acquired by Middle school students) |publisher=Sally Ride Science |accessdate=2012-07-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120801031504/https://moonkam.ucsd.edu/about/moonkam |archivedate=2012-08-01}}</ref>。1999年，她参与了电视剧《{{link-en|天使在人间 (电视剧)|Touched by an Angel|天使在人间}}》第五季的演出<ref>{{cite episode |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0732052 |series=Touched by an Angel |season=5 |number=26 |title=Godspeed |date=1999-05-23 |accessdate=2013-12-16}}</ref>。2003年，她被任命为哥伦比亚航天飞机事故调查委员会的一员。她是萨莉·莱德科技公司的首席执行官，该公司创立于2001年，致力于创建有趣的科学方案和出版物来吸引上小学和初中的学生，特别是女孩<ref name="post">{{cite news|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/07269/820564-85.stm|title=Sally Ride touts science careers for women|accessdate=2007-10-07|work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|first=Dan|last=Majors|date=2007-09-26|archive-date=2012-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312051039/http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/07269/820564-85.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hunt">{{cite web|url=http://www.al.com/news/huntsvilletimes/index.ssf?/base/news/1191230595221160.xml&coll=1 |title=Sally Ride Festival geared for girls |accessdate=2007-10-07 |work=The Huntsville Times |year=2007 |first=Kenneth |last=Kesner |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071120052828/http://www.al.com/news/huntsvilletimes/index.ssf?%2Fbase%2Fnews%2F1191230595221160.xml&coll=1 |archivedate=2007-11-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Busby |first=Guy |url=http://blog.al.com/pr-community-news/2012/07/sally_ride_program_blasts_kids.html |title=Sally Ride program blasts kids into science |publisher=Alabama Media Group |work=Press-Register |location=Mobile, Alabama |date=2012-07-29 |accessdate=2015-05-11 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518091631/http://blog.al.com/pr-community-news/2012/07/sally_ride_program_blasts_kids.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

莱德曾出版七本面向儿童的太空书籍<ref name="SRS SR Books">{{cite web|title=Books |url=http://www.sallyridestore.com/books.html?cat=30 |publisher=Sally Ride Science |accessdate=2012-12-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216075943/http://www.sallyridestore.com/books.html?cat=30 |archivedate=2013-12-16}} ''Mission: Planet Earth'' is two books, making the total five.</ref>，目标是鼓励孩子们学习科学<ref name="pr">{{Cite press release|url=https://www.sallyridescience.com/node/206|title=Sally Ride Science Brings Cutting-Edge Science to the Classroom with New Content Rich Classroom Sets|accessdate=2007-10-07|publisher=Sally Ride Science|date=2007-09-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071010175206/http://sallyridescience.com/node/206|archivedate=2007-10-10}}</ref><ref name="trib">{{cite news|url=http://www.pittsburghlive.com/x/pittsburghtrib/news/cityregion/s_529380.html |title=Sally Ride encourages girls to engineer careers |accessdate=2007-10-07 |work=Pittsburgh Tribune Review |year=2007 |first=Allison M. |last=Heinrichs |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071120051643/http://www.pittsburghlive.com/x/pittsburghtrib/news/cityregion/s_529380.html |archivedate=2007-11-20}}</ref>。

2008年莱德支持[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]成为美国总统<ref name="Space politics">{{cite web |first=Jeff |last=Foust |url=http://www.spacepolitics.com/2008/10/29/sally-ride-endorses-obama/ |title=Sally Ride endorses Obama |accessdate=2010-06-27 |date=2008-10-29 |archive-date=2010-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101006214917/http://www.spacepolitics.com/2008/10/29/sally-ride-endorses-obama/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Ride |first=Sally |title=Inspired kids will reach for stars under Obama |url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/2008-10-29/news/OPride29_1_inspired-space-program-science |date=2008-10-29 |work=Orlando Sentinel |access-date=2015-05-11 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518085222/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/2008-10-29/news/OPride29_1_inspired-space-program-science |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她是美国人类太空飞行计划审查委员会的成员之一。

==个人生活==
[[File:SallyRide2006ByPhilKonstantin.jpg|thumb]]
1982年萨莉·莱德嫁给了资深宇航员[[斯蒂芬·霍利|斯蒂芬·霍利]]，他们于1987年离婚<ref>{{cite news|author=Guy D. Garcia; David E. Thigpen|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,964610,00.html|title=People: June 8, 1987|date=1987-06-08|work=Time|accessdate=2012-07-27|archive-date=2012-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727011935/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,964610,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在莱德去世以后，她的讣告透露，她的伴侣是[[圣迭戈州立大学|圣迭戈州立大学]][[心理学|心理学]]女教授Tam E. O'Shaughnessy，她们是童年好友，都有志成为网球选手<ref name=BrowardTimes>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.browardpalmbeach.com/pulp/2012/07/former_astronaut_sally_ride_re.php|title=Sally Ride Revealed to Be Gay: Her Sister, on Ride's Life, Death, and Desires for Privacy|work=The New Times Broward-Palm Beach|date=2012-07-23|author=Abdill, Rich|accessdate=2012-07-27|archive-date=2012-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728181925/http://blogs.browardpalmbeach.com/pulp/2012/07/former_astronaut_sally_ride_re.php|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=HuffPo>{{cite news |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/23/sally-ride-first-american-woman-female-partner-_n_1696537.html |title=Sally Ride, First American Woman In Space, Revealed To Have Female Partner Of 27 Years |work=The Huffington Post |date=2012-07-23 |accessdate=2012-07-27 |archive-date=2012-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120731024652/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/23/sally-ride-first-american-woman-female-partner-_n_1696537.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Sheets>{{cite news|last=Adams Sheets|first=Connor|title=Tam O'Shaughnessy: About Sally Ride's Partner Of 27 Years|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/365992/20120723/tam-shaughnessy-oshaughnessy-sally-ride-lesbian-partner.htm|newspaper=The International Business Times|date=2012-07-23|accessdate=2012-07-27|archive-date=2012-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120726225713/http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/365992/20120723/tam-shaughnessy-oshaughnessy-sally-ride-lesbian-partner.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sallyridescience.com/node/1059 |title=Talking with Sally Ride and Tam O'Shaughnessy |work=American Library Association |publisher=Sally Ride Science |author=Giorgis, Cyndi |author2=Johnson, Nancy J. |date=2009-03-01 |accessdate=2012-07-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516031027/https://www.sallyridescience.com/node/1059 |archivedate=2013-05-16}}</ref>。O'Shaughnessy长大后成为教师和科普作家。后与莱德一起创办了公司并担任[[首席运营官|首席运营官]]和副总裁<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/24/science/space/sally-ride-trailblazing-astronaut-dies-at-61.html |title=Sally Ride, Trailblazing Astronaut, Dies at 61 |first=Denise |last=Grady |work=The New York Times |date=2012-07-23 |access-date=2012-07-27}}</ref><ref>[https://www.sallyridescience.com/bios/oshaughnessy.html Tam O'Shaughnessy biography on the Sally Ride Science website] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730011254/https://www.sallyridescience.com/bios/oshaughnessy.html |date=2012-07-30 }}. Retrieved July 23, 2012.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://sallyridescience.com/about_us |title=Management Team |publisher=Sally Ride Science |date= |accessdate=2013-11-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005034021/https://www.sallyridescience.com/about_us |archivedate=2013年10月5日 }}</ref>。她们共同合作出版了六本广受好评的儿童科普读物<ref name="SRS SR Books" />。公司透露了她们27年的伴侣关系，并由莱德的妹妹Karen证实。Karen也指出，莱德选择不公开她个人的私人生活，包括关于她的疾病和治疗的事<ref name=BrowardTimes/><ref name=Sheets/>。莱德是已知的第一位[[LGBT|LGBT]]宇航员<ref>{{cite news |title=Sally Ride never hid, was 'just  private' |url=http://www.sfgate.com/politics/joegarofoli/article/Sally-Ride-never-hid-just-private-3732556.php |accessdate=2012-10-29 |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle: SFGate |date=2012-07-25 |first=Joe |last=Garofoli |archive-date=2012-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014172951/http://www.sfgate.com/politics/joegarofoli/article/Sally-Ride-never-hid-just-private-3732556.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenorthstarnews.com/fullstory/story/ernie-banks-was-the-first-black-player-to-sign-with-the-chicago-cubs |title=Ernie Banks Was the First Black Player to Sign with the Chicago Cubs |publisher=North Star News |location=Chicago, Illinois |date=2013-08-13 |access-date=2014-11-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203100638/http://www.thenorthstarnews.com/fullstory/story/ernie-banks-was-the-first-black-player-to-sign-with-the-chicago-cubs |archivedate=2015-02-03}}</ref>。

==去世==
2012年7月23日，在与疾病斗争了17个月后，莱德因[[胰臟癌|胰臟癌]]過世，享年61岁<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-18963939|title=Sally Ride, the first US woman in space, dies aged 61|date=2012-07-23 | publisher = [[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] | accessdate = 2012-07-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Sally Ride, first American woman in space, dies|url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/07/23/us/sally-ride-dead/index.html|accessdate=2012-07-24|publisher=CNN|date=2012-07-24|archive-date=2012-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724002220/http://www.cnn.com/2012/07/23/us/sally-ride-dead/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Sally Ride, first American woman in space, dies at 61|author=William Harwood|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-11386_3-57478314-76/sally-ride-first-american-woman-in-space-dies-at-61/|accessdate=2012-07-23|publisher=CNET|date=2012-07-23|archive-date=2012-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724031558/http://news.cnet.com/8301-11386_3-57478314-76/sally-ride-first-american-woman-in-space-dies-at-61/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = American Woman Who Shattered Space Ceiling | author = Denise Grady | work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/24/science/space/sally-ride-trailblazing-astronaut-dies-at-61.html?pagewanted=print | date = 2012-07-23 | accessdate = 2012-07-24 }}</ref>。[[火化|火化]]后，她的骨灰被安葬在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[圣莫尼卡|圣莫尼卡]]Woodlawn公墓她的父亲旁边<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surfsantamonica.com/ssm_site/the_lookout/news/News-2012/August-2012/08_08_2012_Barrier_Breaking_Astronaut_Interred_at_Santa_Monica_Cemetery.html |title=Barrier-Breaking Astronaut Interred at Santa Monica's Woodlawn Cemetery |publisher=Surfsantamonica.com |date= |accessdate=2013-12-05}}</ref><ref name=FindAGrave>{{cite web|title=Sally Kristen Ride (1951–2012)|url=http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&GRid=94078737|publisher=Find A Grave|accessdate=2012-08-13}}</ref>。

== 奖项及荣誉 ==
[[File:Sally_Ride,_America's_first_woman_astronaut_communicates_with_ground_controllers_from_the_flight_deck_-_NARA_-_541940.jpg|thumb]]与地面控制人员进行联系]]

萨莉·莱德曾经获得众多奖项，包括国家太空协会的冯·布劳恩奖和[[NCAA|NCAA]]的西奥多·罗斯福奖。她入选国家女子名人堂和宇航员名人堂，并两次获得美国宇航局太空飞行奖章。是唯一一位同时参与过[[挑战者号航天飞机|挑战者号航天飞机]]和[[哥伦比亚号航天飞机|哥伦比亚号航天飞机]]事故调查委员会的人。两所美国小学以她的名字命名：分别位于[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]和[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]<ref name="ride1"/>。

1994年，莱德获得塞缪尔·S·比尔德最伟大公共服务个人奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jeffersonawards.org/pastwinners/national |title=National Winners | public service awards |publisher=Jefferson Awards.org |date= |accessdate=2013-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101124043935/http://jeffersonawards.org/pastwinners/national |archive-date=2010-11-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2006年12月6日，[[加利福尼亚州州长|加利福尼亚州州长]][[阿诺·施瓦辛格|阿诺·施瓦辛格]]和夫人[[玛丽娅·施瑞弗尔|玛丽娅·施瑞弗尔]]宣布莱德入选位于加州博物馆的加州名人堂<ref name="hall">{{cite web|url=http://www.californiamuseum.org/exhibits/halloffame/inductee/sally-ride|title=Sally Ride|accessdate=2009-05-27|publisher=The California Museum|year=2006|author=The California Museum|archive-date=2009-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090411013011/https://www.californiamuseum.org/exhibits/halloffame/inductee/sally-ride|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次年，她入选了[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[代顿_(俄亥俄州)|代顿]]的美国国家航空名人堂。

2012年12月17日，NASA 月球任務[[重力回溯及內部結構實驗室|重力回溯及內部結構實驗室]]的兩台探測器 Ebb 和 Flow 在完成任務後撞擊月球表面[[戈尔德施密特环形山|戈尔德施密特环形山]]附近一座撞擊時尚未命名的山。撞擊後 NASA 宣布撞擊地點以萊德命名紀念她參與該任務<ref>[http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2012/dec/HQ_12-438_GRAIL_Impact_Site_Sally_Ride.html NASA's Grail Lunar Impact Site Named for Astronaut Sally Ride] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2012/dec/HQ_12-438_GRAIL_Impact_Site_Sally_Ride.html |date=20121219101736 }} Dec. 17, 2012</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.space.com/18944-nasa-grail-moon-crash-sally-ride.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-18 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207083148/http://www.space.com/18944-nasa-grail-moon-crash-sally-ride.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《飞行》杂志在2013年将莱德列为“航空51英雄”第50名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flyingmag.com/photo-gallery/photos/51-heroes-aviation?pnid=41804|title=51 Heroes of Aviation|work=Flying Magazine|accessdate=2014-11-29|archive-date=2015-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429031708/http://www.flyingmag.com/photo-gallery/photos/51-heroes-aviation?pnid=41804|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==纪念==
2013年4月，[[美国海军|美国海军]]宣布为了纪念萨莉·莱德而将一艘研究船以她的名字命名<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://ucsdnews.ucsd.edu/pressrelease/navy_names_new_scripps_research_vessel_to_honor_the_legacy_of_space_explore |title=Navy Names New Scripps Research Vessel to Honor Legacy of Space Explorer Sally Ride |first=Cindy |last=Clark |date=2013-04-16 |access-date=2015-05-11 |archive-date=2015-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530023356/http://ucsdnews.ucsd.edu/pressrelease/navy_names_new_scripps_research_vessel_to_honor_the_legacy_of_space_explore |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2013年，Janelle Monáe发布了一首名为“萨莉·莱德”（Sally Ride）的歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rock.rapgenius.com/Janelle-monae-sally-ride-lyrics|title=Janelle Monae – Sally Ride Lyrics|access-date=2015-05-11|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203010409/http://rock.rapgenius.com/Janelle-monae-sally-ride-lyrics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同样在2013年，宇航员克里斯·哈德菲尔德和凯瑟琳·科尔曼完成一首名为“Ride on”的歌<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailydot.com/entertainment/chris-hadfield-astronaut-iss-reddit-ama/ |title=8 reasons Chris Hadfield is the coolest astronaut on the Web |first=Michelle |last=Jaworski |date=2013-01-16 |accessdate=2014-02-19 |archive-date=2014-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225013753/http://www.dailydot.com/entertainment/chris-hadfield-astronaut-iss-reddit-ama/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年，航天基金会授予萨莉·莱德最高荣誉--詹姆斯·E·希尔宇宙终身成就奖<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.spacefoundation.org/media/press-releases/neil-armstrong-and-sally-ride-are-2013-general-james-e-hill-lifetime-space |title=Neil Armstrong and Sally Ride Are 2013 General James E. Hill Lifetime Space Achievement Award Honorees |publisher=Space Foundation |location=Colorado Springs, Colorado |date=2012-12-10 |access-date=2013-12-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603040641/http://www.spacefoundation.org/media/press-releases/neil-armstrong-and-sally-ride-are-2013-general-james-e-hill-lifetime-space |archivedate=2013年6月3日 }}</ref>。

2013年5月20日，一场全国悼念萨莉·莱德的仪式在华盛顿特区肯尼迪表演艺术中心举行。就在同一天，美国总统奥巴马宣布，莱德将获得美国平民的最高奖[[总统自由勋章|总统自由勋章]]。2013年11月20日该奖章由莱德的人生伴侣Tam E. O'Shaughnessy在白宫的仪式上代为领取<ref name="Medal of Honor">{{cite news |title=Obama to honor Sally Ride, first US woman in space, with posthumous Medal of Freedom |url=http://www.startribune.com/politics/208202621.html |accessdate=2013-05-21 |newspaper=Star Tribune |date=2013-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328211124/http://www.startribune.com/politics/208202621.html |archive-date=2020-03-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2014年莱德入选了纪念[[LGBT|LGBT]]历史和人物的Legacy Walk<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-gay-plaque-wrigleyville-20141012-story.html|title=Legacy Walk honors LGBT 'guardian angels'|date=2014-10-11|work=Chicago Tribune|accessdate=2015-05-26|archive-date=2015-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529001821/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-gay-plaque-wrigleyville-20141012-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Reynolds |first=Daniel |url=http://www.advocate.com/pride/2014/10/11/photos-7-lgbt-heroes-honored-plaques-chicagos-legacy-walk?page=full |title=PHOTOS: 7 LGBT Heroes Honored With Plaques in Chicago's Legacy Walk |work=The Advocate |accessdate=2015-05-26 |archive-date=2015-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706030243/http://www.advocate.com/pride/2014/10/11/photos-7-lgbt-heroes-honored-plaques-chicagos-legacy-walk?page=full |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月26日萨莉·莱德64周岁诞辰时Google制作了一系列Doodle纪念<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/doodles/sally-rides-64th-birthday|title=Sally Ride's 64th birthday|accessdate=2015-05-26|archive-date=2017-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308080849/https://www.google.com/doodles/sally-rides-64th-birthday|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2017年3月8日亦登上Google慶祝國際婦女節的doodle<ref>{{cite web | title = International Women's Day | url = https://www.google.com/doodles/international-womens-day-2017 | date  = 2017-03-08 | accessdate = 2020-11-21 | language = en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170309082401/https://www.google.com/doodles/international-womens-day-2017# | archive-date = 2017-03-09 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

